verse = \lyricmode {
  For cat -- tle you cause grass to sprout and grow,
and you to man give plants to reap and sow.
You in his bread and wine let him take plea -- sure;
in oil of joy, sup -- plied in rich -- est mea -- sure.
On ce -- dars that you plan -- ted rains pour down;
well wa -- tered are the trees of Leb -- a -- non.
There dwells the stork with birds of every feather;
}
